      h2 The problem
      p Citizens Advice helps millions of people solve their benefits problems every year, both in-person and online.
      p I lead a team that took hundreds of long, complex pages of advice, and replaced them with concise, actionable, and user-centered content.
      p To do this, we needed a deep understanding of our audience and their problems.
