      h2 Understanding the existing content
      p Before we could redesign an expansive area of content, we first needed to understand the key areas covered.
      p We couldn't read through and process hundreds of pages of advice content, so I developed a system to summarise lengthy user journeys.
      p Using this technique, we skimmed through long sections as a group, quickly noting down the key advice offered on each page.

